{"id":9216,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【沉思录】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>改革的行进逻辑与历史脉络</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">——读吴伟《中国</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">80</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年代政治改革的台前幕后》．．董郁玉</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>宪政之我见．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．王建勋</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【亲历记】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>文革末期我在公安部．．．．．．施义之口述　陈　枫整理</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>我是怎么被打成“胡风分子”的．．鲁琪回忆　鲁晓纤整理</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>我所知道的颍上县“特殊案件”．．．．．．．．．王冠群</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【春秋笔】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1933</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年四川兵灾．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．赵晓铃</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【访谈录】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>饶漱石政治秘书谈饶漱石．．．．．．．．．．．．陈邦本</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>我们所知道的陈伯达与江青．．．．．．．王保春　王文耀</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>关于毛泽东遗体保存的回忆．．于书吉口述　程宏采访整理</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【求实篇】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>延安时期的“特产”贸易．．．．．．．．．．．．洪振快</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>读李慎之《关于我的右派罪行的再认识》．．．．．应克复</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>有关高岗“轮流”说的考证．．．．．．．．．．．林蕴晖</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【一家言】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>从一家民间智库说开去．．．．．．．．．．．．．李　锐</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>“正能量”的正解与邪说．．．．．．．．．．．．崔　敏</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>关于对鲁迅的阅读与研究的一点建议．．．．．．．曾彦修</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【忏悔录】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>我上门批判孙大雨．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．武振平</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【人物志】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1949</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年后胡适形象演变．．．．．．．．．．．．．董立功</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>胡绩伟周年祭．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．袁　鹰</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【争鸣录】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>为地质学院造反派说几句话</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">——对《在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&lt;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文汇报</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&gt;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">北办的经历》的一些意见．．．阎长贵</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【品书斋】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>不因人废言，更不可因言废人</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>——《人权与宪政：罗隆基读本》序．．．．．．．郭道晖</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>【海外事】</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>新闻审查浪潮中沉浮的红色诗人．．．．．．．．．李玉贞</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times N